| POST | `/api/purchases/:id/pay` | ✅ | Registrar pago |
| GET | `/api/purchases/payments` | ✅ | Historial pagos |
| GET/POST | `/api/sales` | ✅ | CRUD ventas |
| GET | `/api/sales/:id` | ✅ | Detalle venta |
| GET/POST | `/api/adjustments` | ✅ | Ajustes inventario |
